FOUR members of the same family were killed by lighting on Wednesday. Heavily pregnant mum Nelisiwe Mathenjwa (37) and her children Olwethu (11), Siceluxolo (6) and Asimbonge Mngomezulu (2) were killed instantly when their one-roomed house in Dedefane, northern KZN, was struck by lightning. Sibongile Mngomezulu (13), who was also in the house, was rushed to hospital and is fighting for her life. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstuSspfETI3bX0WEHUgiwlkREGwPHsz8dtzWQM3oFWFpwXsLtGdNDaGl5Be-ieIWDSAHG-X00win2B_KPsmKzRK1W2FnrmkGA8s3X16_1F5qo4f0BuaxhDSP8DrxMYulVC6wPzEZKCDpfIAumFPv_UXsrpRPg5sammmOQSpMkoD-u1P1_UnYp4T63ouySiNzc5fWk7VCwZWq_gavravwMrpbLYoaoI5UK4lYMbli530SLgJ5UfCaJEQ2hjxYCYm8olwWOnYiXpO9IFWLGtN47AHjZyYGfI\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzPP9IT302VhoEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
